"STR       NAME OF THE "STRUCTURE" AND "INITS" ON IT."
"UNITS     NAME OF ALL UNITS "NOT" IN A FILE STRUCTURE."
"BAT       NUMBER OF "BAD" PAGES AND REGIONS FOR A UNIT."
"SATPCBS   NUMBER OF "SAT PCBS"."
