.FILL.JUST
THIS COMMAND IS USED TO ADD A UNIT TO AN ALREADY EXISTING STRUCTURE.
THE PARAMETERS FOR THE UNIT TO BE ADDED WILL AUTOMATICALLY BE SET TO
STANDARD VALUES.  YOU MAY BE ASKED FOR A NEW ID.
.SKIP 1
.NOFILL.NOJUST
"ENTER UNIT NAME TO ADD"
BPA2 (CR) (TYPED IN BY OPERATOR)
