SECOND HOM PAGE CONSISTENCY ERROR
FIRST <BAT PAGE HARDWARE READ ERROR
SECOND <BAT PAGE HARDWARE READ ERROR
FIRST <BAT PAGE CONSISTENCY ERROR
SECOND <BAT PAGE CONSISTENCY ERROR
.PARA
\\
.FILL.JUST
