.indent 8
ever to be left on a drive that is <not
.indent 8
<write <protected.
.SKIP 1
.indent 4
7.  ^the <list command should be run before and after
.indent 8
each <copy command to verify that the right packs are
.indent 8
being used and that the copy was successful.
