.PARA
^INITIALIZE THE <UNITS THAT WILL BE COPIED TO WITH DIFFERENT <SET <ID'S
THAN THE <SOURCE <UNITS.  ^WHEN A <UNIT IS <INITIALIZED, <HOME AND <BAT
