STOPPED.  ^TRY IT AGAIN.  ^IF IT HAPPENS AGAIN, THEN HAVE <NOVADYNE <FE CHECK OUT
THE <UNIT.  ^IF IT
TURNS OUT TO BE A <HEAD CRASH, THE SYSTEM NEEDS TO BE REBUILT.  ^IF
<NOVADYNE <FE ^HARDWARE ^SUPPORT REPORTS THE <UNIT/HDA IS OKAY,
THEN AN ATTEMPT WILL BE MADE TO USE THE <ASP <SAVE PROCEDURES.
^REFER TO <ASP <SAVE/RESTORE PROCEDURES (<PART <IA).
.SKIP 1
