statement that you are entering the FILES dialogue.  All UNITS will
be checked and if any are missing you will receive a statement at this time.
Whenever an HDA is replaced, you will receive the statement LOGICAL UNIT
_#_# MISSING FROM STR DSKB.  This may print out twice and is OKAY.  ^Your
next prompt will be FILES*.  Enter DISSOLVE here and
a YES answer.
